    Type for Fuel Transaction states

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      AUTHORISED
      Transaction has been authorised
      CANCELLED
      Transaction was authorised, but cancelled before any fuel was delivered.
      CLEARED
      Transaction has been cleared
      COMPLETED
      Fuelling has been completed and the transaction is ready to be cleared/sold
      FUELLING
      Transaction is in a fuelling state
      RESERVED
      Transaction has been created by a pump that has been reserved for authorisation in the future.
